    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/74e7682cca8efdcf4189b65adec05b03.avif?t=1763333502\" width=296 height=172 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/43c416f5329865cb281b03f9b7b3b77c.apng?t=1763333502\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/43c416f5329865cb281b03f9b7b3b77c.poster.avif?t=1763333502\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span><strong>STORY</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/ff64bbabc585fa9738f37f2935f06047.apng?t=1763333502\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/ff64bbabc585fa9738f37f2935f06047.poster.avif?t=1763333502\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many years after the events of Crop and Claw have passed. Rumors about the Cult of Atmoss have begun spreading throughout Garden, with their remaining members in motion. A withdrawn dragon named Wend and his friends, along with some mercenary help, must follow the trail of chaos in an foreign realm of the world of Garden and attempt to stop the ominous plot unfolding around them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/4f23f6755c8b41b3fe502f58af6f1952.apng?t=1763333502\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/4f23f6755c8b41b3fe502f58af6f1952.poster.avif?t=1763333502\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/646070470f9d6a36ea1eab521fa85fe9.apng?t=1763333502\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3065270/extras/646070470f9d6a36ea1eab521fa85fe9.poster.avif?t=1763333502\" class=\"bb_img\" width=32 height=32 /></picture></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a custom party of dragons and join story characters throughout an adventure.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragons, everywhere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A non-linear adventure allowing for exploration, routing, and replay-ability.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a dragon.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn-based combat against flora and dragons alike.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple interactions and solutions to puzzles with characters and environments, encouraging exploration and experimentation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dragons. It really is a dragon adventure.</p></li></ul>",
